	<div class="col-md-8 text-left">
		<h3><%= link_to "Where are the MARTA Busses?", blogs_samplejson_path %></h3>
			<p>This nifty little app will show you every single MARTA bus in service at that time. Sometimes, the MARTA API provides some wacky data <%= link_to "(A bus in the middle of the ocean?)", welcome_galapagos_path %>, which can be thoroughly entertaining. Unless, of course the bus you are waiting on is off the coast of the Galapagos Islands.</p>
