		<h3><%= link_to "What is your home REALLY worth?", "http://bakersfieldhomeworth.herokuapp.com" %></h3>
			<p>A realtor in California asked me to create an app that would allow potential customers to find out how much their home was worth. Along with an eye catching design, this app features a database interface, allowing the realtor to see the leads in a datatable.</p>
			<p>Built with <%= link_to "JQuery-Datatables-Rails", "https://github.com/rweng/jquery-datatables-rails" %>, <%= link_to "Rubillow", "https://github.com/synewaves/rubillow" %>, and <%= link_to "Gmaps4Rails", "http://apneadiving.github.io/" %>, this app first asks for the desired address, then shows the user a map of the address and asks them for their contact information. After they enter their info, the value of the house is shown and an email is sentt o the user as well as the realtor.</p>
	</div>
